= Euology to Capital

It has been a year now since we proclaimed the victory of socialism and the defeat of capital following their withdrawal from Germany. Since, we have been working tirelessly to prove our thesis, that this victory be a victory for all workers, and a victory to have been worth struggling and fighting for.

Now, a year later, Germans across the nation look back and ponder how their lives have changed under socialism, if they are truly better than before the revolution. 

